!!!
%html{:lang => "en"}
  %head
    %meta{:charset => "utf-8"}/
    %title 2Date4Love - A different kind of intimacy.
    %meta{:content => "", :name => "description"}/
    %meta{:content => "", :name => "author"}/
    = stylesheet_link_tag 'lounge', 'lounge/home'
    = render 'lounge/shared/fonts'


    /[if gte IE 9]
      :css
        .gradient {
          filter: none;
        }
    /[if lte IE 8]
      :css
        .background-blur {
          background: transparent;
          filter:progid:DXImageTransform.Microsoft.gradient(startColorstr=#7FFFFFFF,endColorstr=#7FFFFFFF);
          zoom: 1
        }
    /[if lt IE 9]
      %script{src: '/assets/html5shiv.js'}
  %body{'cz-shortcut-listen' => true}
    #wrap
      = render 'lounge/shared/topnav'
      .sample-background
        .container
          .row
            = render 'lounge/shared/logo-text'
            - if flash[:alert].present?
              .alert.alert-warning
                = flash[:alert]
            .span6.background-blur
              .span5.message
                %p.welcome Welcome
                %p 2date4loveâ„  is a dating site that enables people who cannot engage in sexual intercourse to meet and experience love, companionship and intimacy.

                %p At 2date4love, we encourage people with this shared commonality to be open to the possibility of finding love and happiness.  This is the community you've been looking for.

                %p We invite you to live love like your life.
                %p.continue.pull-right
                  = link_to new_lounge_home_url(protocol: (Rails.env == 'development' ? 'http': 'https')), class: 'btn btn-large btn-custom2' do
                    %i{class: 'icon-heart'}
                    = 'JOIN TODAY'
          .row
            .span6
              .purple-background
                %p Be among thousands of members on their journey to finding love!

      = render 'lounge/shared/promos'
      = render 'lounge/shared/footer'
      = javascript_include_tag 'main', 'lounge'